Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:

* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.

* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.

snippet.title: Mango Pachcha Teaser | Sanchii | Viveka | KRG Studios | Supriyanvi Studio | CharanRaj | KRG Connects
snippet.description:
The upcoming collaborative biggie of KRG Studios and Supriyanvi Picture Studio #Sanchii01 has revealed its title through a promo of the lead actor Sanchii on account of his birthday. This promo unveils the character of the lead actor and the title of the film. 

"MANGO PACHCHA" is a film that tells the story of an unapologetically ambitious and adventurous man in the city of Mysuru. Based on various real events between the 90â€™s and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.

MOVIE CREDITS
Producers: Priya Sudeep, Karthik & Yogi G Raj
Director: Viveka
Written by: Viveka, Nagbhushan Deshpande
Cast: Sanchith Sanjeev, Kajal Kunder, Prashanth Hiremath, Mayur Patel, Jai Gopinath, Harini Srikanth, Hamsa, Ugramm Manju
Executive Producers: MT Sriram, Abhijith KB
DOP: Shekar Chandra
 Music Director: Charan Raj
Editor: Sharath Vashisht
Art Director: Vishwas Kashyap
Chief Associate Director: Nagbhushan Deshpande
Direction team: Ananya U S, Daniel Raj E, Dhanush K.R, Dr. Rashmith
Camera team: Mariswamy, Madhusudan B R, Sai Raghavendra K, Umesh
Action Director: Ravi Varma, Real Satish, Narsimha C
Chief Art Associate: Raghavendra Rao
Makeup Chief: Ismail(Mysore) 
Stylist: Yogi G Raj
Chief Costumer: Lakshminarayana(Nani) 
Sound Designer: Rajen 
Colorist: Ashik Kusugolli
Online Editor: Sohan Kalaburgi
VFX studios: Fortune FX
Still Photographer: Siddu 
Production Manager: Sudhir K M
PRO: Pink Tickets & Harish Arasu
Publicity Design: Deekshith Sagar
Marketing: KRG Connects
Marketing Team: Suhas Rao & Bindushree 

Music credits 
All tracks composed,arranged and programmed by Charanraj
Vocals:Chethan Naik,Madhwaraj Bharadwaj,Vishak Naglapura,Bhargav HC,Basvanth Rao
Guitars:Sunil Sivester
Music producers:Charanraj and Raghothama N S
Music supervisor:Ananth Kamath M
Recorded @ Audiokraft Studios

Based on various real events between the 90â€™s and 2010, this film will offer great characters, intense drama and unique storyline. It will be a quintessential ode to the city of Mysore through a maverick character. 

The film stars Sanchii aka Junior Kichcha, Malashree, Mayur Patel, Kajal Kunder and others, it's directed by Viveka. The film is produced by Karthik and Yogi G Raj under the banner of KRG Studios in collaboration with Priya Sudeep under the banner of Supriyanvi Picture Studio. The Action-Cut begins from February 10th.
